---
const currentYear = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="bg-primary pt-24 pb-12 px-6 md:px-12 lg:px-32 border-t border-accent/10">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-16 mb-20">
    <div class="col-span-1 md:col-span-2">
      <img src="/images/logos/sub-logo.svg" alt="Layla Sandes" class="h-10 md:h-14 w-auto mb-8" />
      <p class="text-text-muted max-w-sm mb-8 font-sans leading-relaxed text-sm">
        Oferecendo um espaço seguro, ético e sofisticado para sua jornada de autonomia emocional e bem-estar. Atendimento 100% online.
      </p>
      <div class="flex space-x-6">
        <a href="https://www.instagram.com/psi.laylasandes?igsh=MWs2cXo3c21tZ2xrdg%3D%3D" target="_blank" class="text-secondary hover:text-accent transition-all duration-300 transform hover:scale-110" aria-label="Instagram">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-instagram"><rect width="20" height="20" x="2" y="2" rx="5" ry="5"/><path d="M16 11.37A4 4 0 1 1 12.63 8 4 4 0 0 1 16 11.37z"/><line x1="17.5" x2="17.51" y1="6.5" y2="6.5"/></svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h3 class="font-display text-accent uppercase tracking-widest text-sm mb-8">Navegação</h3>
      <ul class="space-y-6 text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] font-medium text-text-muted">
        <li><a href="/#sobre" class="hover:text-secondary transition-colors">A Profissional</a></li>
        <li><a href="/#servicos" class="hover:text-secondary transition-colors">Especialidades</a></li>
        <li><a href="/blog" class="hover:text-secondary transition-colors">Conteúdo</a></li>
        <li><a href="/#contato" class="hover:text-secondary transition-colors">Agendamento</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h3 class="font-display text-accent uppercase tracking-widest text-sm mb-8">Contato</h3>
      <ul class="space-y-6 text-xs text-text-muted font-sans">
        <li class="flex items-center space-x-4">
          <div class="text-secondary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-globe"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><line x1="2" x2="22" y1="12" y2="12"/><path d="M12 2a15.3 15.3 0 0 1 4 10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1-4 10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1-4-10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1 4-10z"/></svg></div>
          <span>Atendimento Online</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-center space-x-4">
          <div class="text-secondary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-phone"><path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-8.63-3.07 19.5 19.5 0 0 1-6-6 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-3.07-8.67A2 2 0 0 1 4.11 2h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 .7 2.81 2 2 0 0 1-.45 2.11L8.09 9.91a16 16 0 0 0 6 6l1.27-1.27a2 2 0 0 1 2.11-.45 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 2.81.7A2 2 0 0 1 22 16.92z"/></svg></div>
          <span>(44) 99158-1606</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-center space-x-4">
          <div class="text-secondary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-mail"><rect width="20" height="16" x="2" y="4" rx="2"/><path d="m22 7-8.97 5.7a1.94 1.94 0 0 1-2.06 0L2 7"/></svg></div>
          <span class="break-all">layla.tamily@hotmail.com</span>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto border-t border-accent/10 pt-10 flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest text-text-muted space-y-4 md:space-y-0">
    <p>© {currentYear} Layla Sandes. Todos os direitos reservados.</p>
    <p>CRP: 08/47025</p>
    <p>Design por <a href="https://www.sitesalphacode.com.br/solucoes/psicologos" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-accent hover:text-secondary transition-colors underline underline-offset-4">Alpha Code</a></p>
  </div>
</footer>
